Welcome to
Fenney Grill!
Where great food
meets the great outdoors!
You will find Fenney Grill conveniently nestled near the Fenney Recreation Center, the Fenney Family Pool, and two Executive Golf Courses.
Hosting you in a casual, drop-in environment*, we serve breakfast, lunch, and dinner daily.
Happy Hour** is 3:00pm - 5:00pm daily.
Breakfast
8:00am - 11:00am  Monday - Saturday
8:00am - 12:00pm  Sunday
Lunch
11:00am - 4:00pm  Monday - Saturday
12:00pm - 4:00pm  Sunday
Dinner
4:00pm - 9:00pm  Sunday - Saturday
*We do not accept reservations or call ahead seating.
**Happy Hour offerings: all bar drinks, House to Top Shelf, are half-price; with the exclusion of frozen beverages.
“Our philosophy is simple:
start local, dream big, and let every dish tell a flavorful story
.”
